OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny residual
OL,6,Fshowery rain this evening soon
OL,7,Fclearing to leave a dry night with
OL,8,Fclear periods, although high level
OL,9,Fcloud increasing later. Winds
OL,10,Fdecreasing with some patchy ground
OL,11,Ffrost possible by dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FChilly start, then bright
OL,14,Fspells through the morning but cloud
OL,15,Fthickens through the afternoon,
OL,16,Fperhaps bringing some patchy light
OL,17,Frain eastwards later. Becoming
OL,18,Fbreezier by the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
